2.1 model + intervention = output

mod %>% ev(amt = 100) %>% mrgsim()
  • A model object mod
    • Everything pertaining to the model that we need to know about to simulate
  • An intervention ev()
  • Simple, easy to implement
    • Build up into more complicated structures
    • See also: data_set
  • A call to mrgsim()
    • This actually carries out the simulation
